      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORE BEER PLEASE (7) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Shepparton in a handy 22.21 beating Cheeky Alessia. Can measure up again. PAW PASCAL (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (22.34) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record here including three wins. Has ability and can atone. ASTON CLEESE (2) goes very well this course and distance starting 11 times for four wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (22.34) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Can feature with the right run. GOLD STRIPES (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
